{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921510/extras/LDI_PAGE_DESCRIPTION_1-14.png?t=1739983561\" /><strong> </strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong> </strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921510/extras/LDI_SINGLE_OR_MULTI-23.png?t=1739983561\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>THIS GAME IS A DEMO<br>SINGLE OR CO-OP SURVIVAL ADVENTURE GAME!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this adventure, you can progress alone or with your friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You must fight a challenging battle to escape the island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921510/extras/LDI_NIGHT_GIF_1.gif?t=1739983561\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>SURVIVAL</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You must fight against many elements like hunger, thirst, temperature, sleep deprivation, and creature attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921510/extras/LDI_GIF_3.gif?t=1739983561\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>ROAD TRIP WITH A VAN</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect parts to repair your van and hit the road!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your vehicle can overheat, get flat tires, break down, or run out of fuel. Despite all this, you must keep going! Your van includes a water tank, a fridge, and a stove for cooking.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>VEHICLE UPGRADES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can upgrade your vehicle\u2019s wheels and engine, expand storage space, and add extra parts to protect against creature attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com